---
import RealestateLayout from '../../layouts/RealestateLayout.astro';
import CtaButton from '../../components/CtaButton.astro';
import NewsletterSignup from '../../components/NewsletterSignup.astro';
---

<RealestateLayout
  title="Buy a Home in Toronto and the GTA | Cory Wong, Real Estate Agent | Trustwell Realty"
  description="Buying in Toronto, Markham, or Richmond Hill? Cory Wong offers buyer representation across the GTA. Free consultation. Trustwell Realty Inc., Brokerage."
  canonicalPath="/buy"
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Buy in the GTA</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__subtitle">
        Buying a home in Toronto, Markham, or Richmond Hill takes preparation and the right
        representation. Cory will guide you from pre-approval to closing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What Cory Provides</h2>
      <div class="services-intro">
        <p>
          Working with a buyer's agent costs you nothing. The seller's brokerage covers both
          sides of the commission. You get an agent whose job is to look out for you.
        </p>
        <p>Services include:</p>
        <ul class="services-list">
          <li>Buyer consultation to define your goals, budget, and timeline</li>
          <li>MLS access across the GTA</li>
          <li>Showings in Toronto, Markham, Richmond Hill, and surrounding areas</li>
          <li>Offer preparation and negotiation support</li>
          <li>Coordination with your mortgage broker, lawyer, and home inspector</li>
          <li>Guidance from first search to closing day</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Cory also works with buyers in Peel, York, and Durham regions. If you're searching
          across the GTA, one agent covers it all.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>The GTA Buying Process</h2>
      <div class="process-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">1</span>
          <h3>Get Pre-Approved</h3>
          <p>Before you search, get pre-approved. Your mortgage broker reviews your income, credit, and down payment and gives you a clear budget ceiling. First-time buyers should ask about the First Home Savings Account (FHSA) before starting.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">2</span>
          <h3>Define Your Criteria</h3>
          <p>Location, size, commute, and price range set the parameters. The GTA covers dozens of distinct neighbourhoods. Cory helps you prioritize so your search is focused.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">3</span>
          <h3>Search and Showings</h3>
          <p>New listings come to you as they hit MLS. When something fits, Cory books the showing. In the GTA, well-priced properties move quickly. Preparation matters.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">4</span>
          <h3>Make an Offer</h3>
          <p>Before you offer, Cory prepares a comparative market analysis showing what similar homes have sold for. Offer price, conditions, and terms are your decisions. Cory gives you the data to decide clearly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">5</span>
          <h3>Due Diligence</h3>
          <p>A conditional offer gives you time to arrange a home inspection, review the status certificate (for condos), and confirm your mortgage. These conditions protect your deposit and your decision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step__number">6</span>
          <h3>Close</h3>
          <p>Your lawyer handles the legal transfer. Closing costs in Ontario typically range from 1.5 to 3 percent of the purchase price. They include land transfer tax, legal fees, and title insurance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do I need a buyer's agent?</summary>
          <p>Not legally. Without one, you're negotiating against the listing agent, who works for the seller. Buyer representation is free to you.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>How long does buying take?</summary>
          <p>From pre-approval to closing, plan for 2 to 4 months. Your timeline depends on how specific your criteria are and how fast the market is moving in your target area.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What is the stress test?</summary>
          <p>Canada's mortgage stress test requires you to qualify at a rate above your actual mortgage rate. Your mortgage broker will apply the current qualifying rate to your application. It affects your maximum purchase price.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Should I buy before selling my current home?</summary>
          <p>This depends on your finances and risk tolerance. There are strategies for both approaches. Cory will help you think through the options. For advice specific to your situation, speak with your mortgage broker and lawyer.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>What is a buyer representation agreement?</summary>
          <p>Under Ontario's REBBA, your agent must have a signed buyer representation agreement with you before showing properties. It sets out the agent's obligations and the terms of the relationship. Cory will walk you through it before signing.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you work with new construction buyers?</summary>
          <p>Yes. New construction comes with different timelines, larger deposit structures, and builder contracts written in the builder's favour. Cory will review what you're signing before you commit.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you cover areas outside Toronto, Markham, and Richmond Hill?</summary>
          <p>Yes. Cory also works with buyers in Peel, York, and Durham regions. Contact Cory to discuss your search area.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="lead-form-section" id="inquiry">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Tell Me What You're Looking For</h2>
      <p class="lead-form-section__subtitle">Share your preferences and I'll follow up with relevant listings and insights.</p>
      <form class="lead-form" id="buyer-form" data-form-type="buyer">
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="buyer-name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="buyer-name" name="name" required autocomplete="name" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="buyer-email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="buyer-email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="buyer-budget">Budget Range</label>
            <select id="buyer-budget" name="budget">
              <option value="">Select a range</option>
              <option value="under-500k">Under $500,000</option>
              <option value="500k-750k">$500,000 - $750,000</option>
              <option value="750k-1m">$750,000 - $1,000,000</option>
              <option value="1m-1.5m">$1,000,000 - $1,500,000</option>
              <option value="1.5m-plus">$1,500,000+</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-field">
            <label for="buyer-timeline">Timeline</label>
            <select id="buyer-timeline" name="timeline">
              <option value="">Select timeline</option>
              <option value="asap">As soon as possible</option>
              <option value="1-3months">1-3 months</option>
              <option value="3-6months">3-6 months</option>
              <option value="6-12months">6-12 months</option>
              <option value="exploring">Just exploring</option>
            </select>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="buyer-neighbourhoods">Preferred Neighbourhoods</label>
          <input type="text" id="buyer-neighbourhoods" name="neighbourhoods" placeholder="e.g., Markham, Richmond Hill, North York" />
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="buyer-notes">Anything else I should know?</label>
          <textarea id="buyer-notes" name="notes" rows="3"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Send Inquiry</button>
        <p class="form-status" id="buyer-form-status" aria-live="polite"></p>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Ready to Start Your Search?</h2>
      <p>Book a free 30-minute consultation. You'll come away with a clear picture of the market and a plan for next steps.</p>
      <CtaButton href="/contact" label="Book a Consultation" variant="primary" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <NewsletterSignup heading="Get the GTA Market Report Each Month" />
</RealestateLayout>

<script>
  const form = document.getElementById('buyer-form') as HTMLFormElement;
  const status = document.getElementById('buyer-form-status') as HTMLElement;

  form?.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    status.textContent = 'Sending...';
    status.className = 'form-status';

    const data = Object.fromEntries(new FormData(form));

    try {
      const res = await fetch('/api/lead', {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
        body: JSON.stringify({ ...data, type: 'buyer' }),
      });

      if (res.ok) {
        status.textContent = 'Thank you! I\'ll be in touch soon.';
        status.classList.add('form-status--success');
        form.reset();
      } else {
        throw new Error('Failed');
      }
    } catch {
      status.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Please email directly or try again.';
      status.classList.add('form-status--error');
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .page-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .services-intro {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .services-intro p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .services-list {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .services-list li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .services-list li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.5rem;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .process-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    background: #f5f5f4;
  }

  .process-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .process-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .step {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 3.5rem;
  }

  .step__number {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .faq-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .faq-item p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .lead-form-section {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    background: #f5f5f4;
  }

  .lead-form-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .lead-form-section__subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .lead-form {
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .form-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .form-field label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .form-field input,
  .form-field select,
  .form-field textarea {
    padding: 0.625rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field select:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.1);
  }

  .form-submit {
    padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: #ffffff;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .form-submit:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .form-status {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    min-height: 1.25rem;
  }

  .form-status--success {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .form-status--error {
    color: #dc2626;
  }

  .cta-banner {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-banner h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .cta-banner p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: 32rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .form-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
